{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775888777936,"sessionID":"ses_284c9343cffeiZFXI2p5Yhu5Cq","part":{"id":"prt_d7b38129f001bmV2uOF1bjZ20X","messageID":"msg_d7b374713001YU4fKBt5E54sPc","sessionID":"ses_284c9343cffeiZFXI2p5Yhu5Cq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/tests.md","content":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Authentication Tests\n- `test_auth_loads_from_file`: Credentials load from file\n- `test_auth_falls_back_to_env`: Env var fallback works\n- `test_auth_missing_raises_error`: Error on missing credentials\n\n### Registry Client Tests\n- `test_upload_sends_correct_headers`: Headers include auth\n- `test_upload_streams_file`: File streamed correctly\n- `test_upload_reports_progress`: Progress callback invoked\n- `test_upload_handles_errors`: Error responses handled\n\n### Command Tests\n- `test_publish_validates_args`: Invalid args rejected\n- `test_publish_checks_file_exists`: Missing file reported\n- `test_publish_dry_run_no_upload`: Dry run skips upload\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Happy Path\n- `test_publish_success`: Complete publish flow\n- `test_publish_with_progress`: Progress shown correctly\n\n### Error Scenarios\n- `test_publish_auth_failure`: 401 handled gracefully\n- `test_publish_invalid_package`: Validation errors reported\n- `test_publish_network_error`: Connection failures handled\n\n## Test Data\n- Valid package file fixture\n- Invalid package file fixture\n- Mock registry server\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-020/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/tests.md","exists":false,"